        },
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "describing",
          "value": "The tangent bundle is charted on `ModelProd H E` (so locally `H × E`, dimension `2 dim M` in the finite-dimensional case), but there is no `finrank`/dimension theorem stating `dim (TangentBundle I M) = 2 * dim M`.",
          "format": "text/plain"
        }
      ],
      "target": {
        "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tangent_bundle?oldid=1351233929",
