        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "describing",
          "value": "A smooth vector field is `Cₛ^n⟮I; E, TangentSpace I⟯` = `ContMDiffSection I E n (TangentSpace I)`, a `C^n` section assigning `x ↦ v x ∈ TangentSpace I x`; unbundled vector fields appear as `Π x, TangentSpace I x` throughout `Mathlib.Geometry.Manifold.VectorField`.",
          "format": "text/plain"
        }
      ],
      "target": {
        "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tangent_bundle?oldid=1351233929",
