        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "describing",
          "value": "A 1-form is represented as a section `Π x, TangentSpace I x →L[𝕜] 𝕜` of the (implicit) cotangent bundle; `extDerivFun g` produces the exterior derivative of a scalar function as such a section. There is no named `CotangentBundle` nor a general space of differential 1-forms / differential forms.",
          "format": "text/plain"
        }
      ],
      "target": {
