          "value": "Since `TangentBundle I M` is itself a `C^n` manifold (via `IsManifold (IB.prod 𝓘(𝕜,F)) n (TotalSpace ...)` and model `I.tangent`), the double tangent bundle `TangentBundle I.tangent (TangentBundle I M)` is expressible, but there is no dedicated `SecondOrderTangentBundle` definition.",
